title: 236: Our Quarantine Activities | Ear Biscuits Ep. 236
description:
From diving into TikTok to a 2000 piece puzzle, there are a plethora of activities that people are engaging in to pass the time. Listen to R&L discuss some strange, unusual, or completely common things people are doing to pass the time as well as what they themselves have been up to on this episode of Ear Biscuits!
